<p>
Dear <%= @request.user.first_name %>,
</p>

<p>
This notice is to inform you that your request for appointment to <%= @request.requestable %> has been approved.
</p>

<% if @request.memberships.any? %>
<p>
You have been appointed to the following <%=
  [ @request.memberships.count, @request.enrollments.count ].max > 1 ? 'positions' : 'position' %>:
</p>

<ul>
<%= render :partial => 'membership', :collection => @request.memberships %>
</ul>
<% else %>
<p>
You have not been appointed to any positions as a result of this request.  This is most likely for reasons communicated to you or by you separately from this notice.
</p>
<% end %>

<p>
If you have additional questions or concerns regarding this notice or your appointment, please contact <%= Staffing::Application.app_config['defaults']['authority']['contact_name'] %> &lt;<%= Staffing::Application.app_config['defaults']['authority']['contact_email'] %>&gt;.
</p>

<p>
Best regards,
</p>

<p>
<%= Staffing::Application.app_config['defaults']['authority']['contact_name'] %>
</p>

